Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.63,0:02:15.82,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}你还是一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.16,0:02:19.19,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我还是一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.31,0:02:25.52,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}倘若能彼此交心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.92,0:02:33.86,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}自那天起 四季更替时光流转
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:39.65,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我只想说 谢谢你伴我至今
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.04,0:02:47.86,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}呵着白气 朝向狭窄的小巷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.99,0:02:53.25,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}你温暖的手使劲拉着我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.35,0:02:55.21,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}不断前行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.29,0:02:58.41,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}好想马上就亲吻你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.66,0:03:02.11,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}躲在自动售货机背后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.37,0:03:05.56,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}害羞地凝视对方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.80,0:03:11.00,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}温柔的心情洋溢胸口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.26,0:03:14.53,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}你还是一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.70,0:03:17.98,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我还是一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.32,0:03:23.42,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}倘若能彼此交心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:25.57,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我们便能融为一体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.65,0:03:28.77,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}与一份小小幸福的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:32.32,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}似乎就在触手可及的前方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.52,0:03:35.05,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}能变得如此温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.08,0:03:38.01,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}全因有你
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------EDCN5-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.52,0:23:46.72,EDCN6,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}霓虹灯的蓝光 妆点着人行道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.11,0:23:54.35,EDCN6,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}热闹的人群中 我独自伫立
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.54,0:23:58.63,EDCN6,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}写满快乐的一张张笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.76,0:24:03.12,EDCN6,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}相互依偎的一对对恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.37,0:24:07.56,EDCN6,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}对此刻的我而言 这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.69,0:24:12.48,EDCN6,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}都太过耀眼 而不能直视
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.65,0:24:19.70,EDCN6,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}有人会爱我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.76,0:24:30.09,EDCN6,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}谁来察觉藏在坚强背后的我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.33,0:24:36.02,EDCN6,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}真的能获得自由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.28,0:24:39.12,EDCN6,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}请告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.28,0:24:46.45,EDCN6,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}冬日的街道上 误入人间的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.86,0:24:56.10,EDCN6,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}正温柔地轻声叹息
