Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.40,0:00:20.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.02,0:00:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.69,0:00:24.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,创设祭的准备工作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.55,0:00:27.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就剩下装点圣诞树了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.80,0:00:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于能顺利迎来创设祭了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.11,0:00:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很感谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.77,0:00:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在说还太早了吧 绚辻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.20,0:00:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是 等迎来以后再谢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.78,0:00:46.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.30,0:00:48.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.43,0:00:52.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就到创设祭了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.06,0:00:55.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起奋斗到底吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.28,0:00:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.11,0:01:03.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不在了？什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.27,0:01:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是说你有双重人格
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.48,0:01:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而到昨天为止的人格消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.07,0:01:10.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.50,0:01:12.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双重人格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.87,0:01:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有趣的解释呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.28,0:01:16.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 错了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.09,0:01:18.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.90,0:01:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 到昨天为止的她已经消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.62,0:01:24.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住这点就行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.67,0:01:26.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 大家还等着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.95,0:01:29.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回去做创设祭的准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.80,0:01:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,橘？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.70,0:01:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么在发呆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.55,0:01:38.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…没有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.97,0:01:40.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.26,0:01:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 橘也来和大家一起装点圣诞树吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.08,0:01:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.74,0:01:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还得最后检查一遍备用品呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.12,0:01:52.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是执行委员的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:54.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先去做那个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.18,0:01:58.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:03.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的绚辻很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.80,0:02:05.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.80,0:02:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且班上的气氛也活跃起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.35,0:02:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TXTA-----------------------------------
