Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.35,0:04:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有看我致辞吗 橘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.69,0:04:41.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 说得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.93,0:04:43.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:47.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣诞树真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:49.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:52.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绚辻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:56.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快来～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:04:59.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了～等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.63,0:05:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟弥生她们约好了空余时间一起逛的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:05.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.69,0:05:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.89,0:05:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.15,0:05:09.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.21,0:05:13.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那等会儿见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.26,0:05:22.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.90,0:05:24.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸡蛋和鱼糕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.77,0:05:26.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.36,0:05:35.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可爱的小兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.99,0:05:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃掉你～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.43,0:05:43.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜…请饶命啊～官老爷～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:46.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 下一位是7号佳丽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.90,0:05:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连续两届蝉联圣诞小姐冠军
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:51.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家引颈以待的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森岛遥学姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.16,0:05:59.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好大胆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差点就要破底线啦 森岛学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 这身衣服真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.82,0:06:15.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我穿应该是在允许范围内的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:20.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 都怪遥突然间说要参赛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看她那么开心 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.52,0:06:27.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.09,0:06:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请·多·关·照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.08,0:06:31.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:37.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是森岛学姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.17,0:06:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟是大美人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.09,0:06:41.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3连冠要达成了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绚辻 你是不是也觉得森岛学姐会赢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难说 大家都很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:50.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道选哪个好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.28,0:06:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 弥生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.58,0:06:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回去做执行委员的工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:55.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.61,0:06:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庆功宴上见咯
