Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 点心每人一个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.26,0:07:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…别摸奇怪的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！那里手别伸进去！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.25,0:07:09.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小梨穗很受孩子们欢迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.25,0:07:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是个好女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.63,0:07:15.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊拉 看起来美味的甜酒呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高桥老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.11,0:07:18.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不能给老师喝哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 去年就是稍微闹了一下 喝一杯没问题～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:26.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能相信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.03,0:07:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惨剧的预感
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//-----------------以上取自smoothluv@苍雪论坛翻译BDRip字幕------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.96,0:07:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:35.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 梨穗子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.61,0:07:37.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.27,0:07:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巡逻顺便来看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.90,0:07:40.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟约好了的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.69,0:07:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很旺嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.95,0:07:44.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托你的福
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.87,0:07:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯一也喝点东西再走嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.79,0:07:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要茶还是甜酒？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.75,0:07:51.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就免了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:53.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.58,0:07:56.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯一 你好像没什么精神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.72,0:07:59.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,0:08:00.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小梨穗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子们都在等吃点心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…不好意思 马上来～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:09.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先失陪啦 纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:10.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油哦 梨穗子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:17.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.59,0:08:20.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 樱井
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我过来玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.62,0:08:22.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香苗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.73,0:08:25.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 很受欢迎嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绚辻 为什么会变成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.17,0:09:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.63,0:09:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何我会心乱如麻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:13.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅原
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.20,0:09:14.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.06,0:09:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想不开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.71,0:09:21.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别因为今年也交不上女友就纵火啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.43,0:09:23.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用这么自暴自弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 原来是小学时收到的情书啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.16,0:09:39.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过为啥现在才烧掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.36,0:09:40.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.97,0:09:43.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论喜欢还是讨厌一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.18,0:09:46.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都会觉得自己很逊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:47.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:51.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我打死也没给人家一个答复
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.06,0:09:55.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了现在才后悔 太浪费了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.12,0:09:59.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以啊 不能一直都留恋着那时嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.79,0:10:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索性烧了 一了百了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.32,0:10:04.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真干脆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:06.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干脆毛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在后悔得要命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.21,0:10:10.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后悔…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.74,0:10:14.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 哥们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.16,0:10:22.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.09,0:10:25.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然说过今年圣诞要加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.42,0:10:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不像话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.86,0:10:32.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平安夜还没结束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.89,0:10:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得自己不像话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.72,0:10:36.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就只有去行动了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:39.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别到时跟我一样后悔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.68,0:10:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢啦 梅原
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.47,0:10:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.17,0:10:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.09,0:10:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为啥会没女友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.16,0:10:54.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼泪哗哗的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.16,0:11:00.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.89,0:11:02.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能收到绚辻的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.89,0:11:20.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给 圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.97,0:11:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面是糖果哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.57,0:11:25.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Comment: 0,0:01:19.00,0:01:19.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TXTB-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.78,0:11:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至此 第57届创设祭宣告结束
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.61,0:11:47.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衷心感谢大家的光临
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.88,0:11:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿各位过个美妙的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 为了庆祝第57届创设祭圆满成功
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.34,0:11:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干杯！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.76,0:12:01.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干杯！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.63,0:12:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是大家的功劳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.78,0:12:11.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.59,0:12:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绚辻也很卖力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.69,0:12:16.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忙是忙 不过挺好玩的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.35,0:12:17.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.64,0:12:21.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说祭典是准备过程最开心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.02,0:12:23.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然没错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.49,0:12:24.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么辛苦准备的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了有点寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.27,0:12:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰 你这选美比赛司仪很有型哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.30,0:12:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 不过我想作为佳丽参加呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:40.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 今年森岛学姐顺利达成3连冠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.60,0:12:43.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没去打工而来当司仪也值了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.73,0:12:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 橘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.20,0:12:48.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.57,0:12:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庆功宴已经开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:52.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.52,0:12:55.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你看到就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.73,0:12:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的圣诞老人装束很受欢迎哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.70,0:13:01.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 绚辻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:03.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.66,0:13:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.65,0:13:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么话跟我说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.84,0:13:11.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:14.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,橘？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.60,0:13:22.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没向大家道谢完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.24,0:13:23.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先回教室了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.25,0:13:30.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.90,0:13:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅原 怎么这么晚才来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.17,0:13:35.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:39.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过主角都是最后登场的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:41.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说谁是主角啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.87,0:13:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,创设祭基本上都没见到人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.39,0:13:46.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点杂事要处理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正又是被人甩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 橘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.83,0:13:57.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.59,0:13:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也对橘…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.62,0:14:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.55,0:14:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我圣诞节有过不好的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.09,0:14:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对这个时期很不适应
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.48,0:14:11.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去年也没参加创设祭 逃出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:16.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 觉得不能一直这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.99,0:14:19.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才报名当执行委员
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想在今年圣诞加把劲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.83,0:14:26.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是就跟绚辻一起干活
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.13,0:14:28.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.05,0:14:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我捡到你的笔记本
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.57,0:14:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后 被你带去神社
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.66,0:14:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道你有那一面后真的吃了一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.64,0:14:41.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.52,0:14:44.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很庆幸自己知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.37,0:14:50.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被你斥责着工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:53.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很忙很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.24,0:14:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也觉得很充实
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.25,0:14:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 连对圣诞感到不适应的功夫也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.95,0:15:02.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不觉间似乎没了负担 我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.66,0:15:06.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能我从那时起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.33,0:15:09.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就喜欢上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.71,0:15:11.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,橘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.24,0:15:12.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.51,0:15:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌现在的我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.44,0:15:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不讨厌哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:20.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也喜欢现在的你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.51,0:15:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:23.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.10,0:15:27.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前那个固执的你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.72,0:15:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有装乖的你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.60,0:15:32.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.79,0:15:34.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:38.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你不要说「消失了」这种寂寞的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.50,0:15:41.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有什么地方做得不够的 希望你能骂我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.70,0:15:43.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就想说这些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.14,0:15:45.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:46.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:50.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绚辻？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.55,0:16:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.08,0:16:03.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这算什么意思嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.91,0:16:05.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你说了那种话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.95,0:16:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才决定让自己消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.10,0:16:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.80,0:16:16.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢的绚辻就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.04,0:16:39.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.90,0:16:43.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才是什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.79,0:16:48.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高桥老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:49.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.88,0:16:52.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才这附近发出很大一声响
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.81,0:16:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.94,0:16:58.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喝了甜酒有点醉 摔倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:17:01.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不小心喊了声痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.51,0:17:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵到你真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.14,0:17:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 田中老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.55,0:17:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也去庆功吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.73,0:17:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃？啊…好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.79,0:17:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是 拿你们没辙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.89,0:17:15.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我送的圣诞礼物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:18.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊 我也想要个男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃？那首先要控制喝酒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.31,0:17:32.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:34.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.77,0:17:37.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本就是你不对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.31,0:17:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.25,0:17:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从背后抱女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.93,0:17:42.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是性骚扰哦 性骚扰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.43,0:17:46.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.09,0:17:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能听我说点事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.14,0:17:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.22,0:17:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.40,0:17:54.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.51,0:17:58.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一天 我知道圣诞老人是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.82,0:18:01.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且事实还摆在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.22,0:18:02.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.65,0:18:04.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是经常有嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.57,0:18:07.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到父母把礼物放进袜子的情景
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.76,0:18:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像这种
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.19,0:18:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的话就更惨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.25,0:18:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么个惨法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.96,0:18:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.77,0:18:17.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.18,0:18:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道没有圣诞老人以后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.50,0:18:22.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我下了个决心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.35,0:18:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「要当圣诞老人」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.25,0:18:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明知道成不了正牌的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.04,0:18:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也想做些类似的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.03,0:18:36.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,类似的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.65,0:18:37.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.70,0:18:42.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在平安夜 送幸福给大家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你当执行委员的理由？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:48.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.78,0:18:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用自己的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.31,0:18:53.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让大家多少过个幸福的圣诞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.09,0:18:56.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很美好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.34,0:18:58.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:19:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小时候 我来辉日东高中创设祭玩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.14,0:19:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.11,0:19:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是经自己的手 让创设祭成功的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.97,0:19:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就令大家都幸福了么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.39,0:19:14.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让大家幸福的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.54,0:19:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不觉间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.78,0:19:23.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就变成为了满足我自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.31,0:19:25.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都很开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.13,0:19:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过小孩子最明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这个版本的圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.41,0:19:35.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很受大人欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.02,0:19:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是小孩子却不亲近我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.72,0:19:44.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强如绚辻 也骗不了小孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.09,0:19:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.49,0:19:53.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绚辻 圣诞还没结束哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.96,0:19:55.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.18,0:19:58.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明年 后年 圣诞都会到来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.89,0:20:02.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次圣诞都让大家幸福不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.12,0:20:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.85,0:20:05.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.03,0:20:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:08.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.74,0:20:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你也让我幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.74,0:20:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是女生的台词吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.75,0:20:19.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.63,0:20:21.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.36,0:20:26.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 头发都乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.74,0:20:29.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 我自己能弄好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.63,0:20:31.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.75,0:20:48.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也喜欢你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.58,0:20:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.92,0:20:52.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是契约么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.63,0:20:55.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是约定
Comment: 0,0:01:19.00,0:01:19.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------INCN-----------------------------------
