Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.34,0:21:08.28,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,1500)\be2}I love you forever with you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.28,0:21:25.32,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}那张纯真的笑脸 只有我才知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.47,0:21:30.22,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}你竟然如此地爱撒娇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.47,0:21:32.85,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}搞不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.05,0:21:40.09,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}你到底是顽童还是帅哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.22,0:21:45.19,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}永不放开你的大手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.31,0:21:50.23,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}以前曾发誓最后一次恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.31,0:21:54.92,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\be2\pos(424,470)}如今却想把这个秘密永藏于心…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.23,0:22:05.03,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}…我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.18,0:22:08.61,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}初次体会到的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.98,0:22:12.67,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Oh 我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.77,0:22:15.26,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}永远永远
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.38,0:22:20.44,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)\be2}此情不变
