Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.32,0:21:55.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,470)}这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.71,0:21:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题 就一下下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.99,0:22:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.19,0:22:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这棵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.47,0:22:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,充满爸爸跟妈妈的回忆的树
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.42,0:22:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.70,0:22:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸妈妈就是在这里许下重要约定的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.99,0:22:45.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约定？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.37,0:22:46.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么约定？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.80,0:22:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.50,0:22:51.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 词
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.19,0:22:52.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.44,0:22:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.30,0:22:57.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很幸福哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.83,0:23:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我也要亲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.36,0:23:06.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望全世界的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.43,0:23:08.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在今天这个好日子里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.71,0:23:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都获得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.89,0:23:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像我们一样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.71,0:23:14.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.62,0:23:28.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------NEXT-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.86,0:25:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集预告
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.92,0:25:03.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老哥 有件事想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.37,0:25:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.88,0:25:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,某一天 素未谋面的可爱女生
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.40,0:25:07.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然向你表白 会怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.31,0:25:08.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 这是什么问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.46,0:25:10.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少说废话 快回答
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.12,0:25:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说 你会怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.61,0:25:15.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 可爱女生向自己表白当然开心
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.42,0:25:18.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不了解她的话 不能答应吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.59,0:25:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦～以老哥来说
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.42,0:25:22.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这回答意外地正经啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.42,0:25:24.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一集 真相
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.29,0:25:27.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被甩的那年冬天的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.09,0:25:28.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又要苏醒了
